{"data":[{"name":"96:1","price":"1. (நபியே! அனைத்தையும்) படைத்த உமது இறைவனின் பெயரால் (அவனது கட்டளைகள் அடங்கிய திரு குர்ஆனை) ஓதுவீராக!","arabic":"ٱقۡرَأۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6107,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"iq'ra bi-is'mi rabbika alladhī khalaqa ","translations":["Read","in (the) name","(of) your Lord","the One Who","created ","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["iq'ra","bi-is'mi","rabbika","alladhī","khalaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,830],[2,830,1370],[3,1370,2250],[4,2250,3050],[5,3050,4325]]}},{"name":"96:2","price":"2. அவனே மனிதனை இரத்தக்கட்டியிலிருந்து படைக்கிறான்.","arabic":"خَلَقَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ مِنۡ عَلَقٍ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6108,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"khalaqa al-insāna min ʿalaqin ","translations":["He created","man","from","a clinging substance","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["khalaqa","al-insāna","min","ʿalaqin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,760],[2,760,2660],[3,2660,3100],[4,3100,4385]]}},{"name":"96:3","price":"3. (நபியே! மேலும்) நீர் ஓதுவீராக! உமது இறைவன் மாபெரும் கொடையாளி!","arabic":"ٱقۡرَأۡ وَرَبُّكَ ٱلۡأَكۡرَمُ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6109,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"iq'ra warabbuka al-akramu ","translations":["Read","and your Lord","(is) the Most Generous","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["iq'ra","warabbuka","al-akramu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,1810],[3,1810,3345]]}},{"name":"96:4","price":"4. அவன்தான் எழுதுகோலைக் கொண்டு (எழுதக்) கற்றுக் கொடுத்தான்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي عَلَّمَ بِٱلۡقَلَمِ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6110,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī ʿallama bil-qalami ","translations":["The One Who","taught","by the pen","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","ʿallama","bil-qalami",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,1910],[3,1910,2865]]}},{"name":"96:5","price":"5. (அதன் மூலம்) மனிதன் அறியாதவற்றை எல்லாம் அவனுக்குக் கற்றுக் கொடுக்கிறான்.","arabic":"عَلَّمَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ مَا لَمۡ يَعۡلَمۡ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6111,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿallama al-insāna mā lam yaʿlam ","translations":["Taught","man","what","not","he knew","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿallama","al-insāna","mā","lam","yaʿlam",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,900],[2,900,3010],[3,3010,3350],[4,3350,3770],[5,3770,4615]]}},{"name":"96:6","price":"6, 7. (இவ்வாறிருந்தும்,) மனிதன் (அவனுக்கு நன்றி செலுத்துவதற்குப் பதிலாகத்) தன்னை (இறைவனின் அருளிலிருந்து) தேவையற்றவன் என்று மெய்யாகவே எண்ணிக்கொண்டு, அவனுக்கு மாறு செய்கிறான்.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ لَيَطۡغَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6112,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā inna al-insāna layaṭghā ","translations":["Nay","Indeed","man","surely transgresses","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","inna","al-insāna","layaṭghā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2380],[2,2380,3430],[3,3430,5480],[4,5480,7055]]}},{"name":"96:7","price":"6, 7. (இவ்வாறிருந்தும்,) மனிதன் (அவனுக்கு நன்றி செலுத்துவதற்குப் பதிலாகத்) தன்னை (இறைவனின் அருளிலிருந்து) தேவையற்றவன் என்று மெய்யாகவே எண்ணிக்கொண்டு, அவனுக்கு மாறு செய்கிறான்.","arabic":"أَن رَّءَاهُ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6113,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"an raāhu is'taghnā ","translations":["That","he sees himself","self-sufficient","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["an","raāhu","is'taghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,300],[2,300,1320],[3,1320,2525]]}},{"name":"96:8","price":"8. நிச்சயமாக உமது இறைவன் பக்கம்தான் (அவன்) மீள வேண்டும்.","arabic":"إِنَّ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ ٱلرُّجۡعَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6114,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ilā rabbika al-ruj'ʿā ","translations":["Indeed","to","your Lord","(is) the return","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ilā","rabbika","al-ruj'ʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,1900],[3,1900,2700],[4,2700,3905]]}},{"name":"96:9","price":"9-10. (நபியே!) ஓர் அடியார் தொழுதால், அதைத் தடை செய்கின்றவனை நீர் (கவனித்துப்) பார்த்தீரா?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يَنۡهَىٰ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6115,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ara-ayta alladhī yanhā ","translations":["Have you seen","the one who","forbids","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["ara-ayta","alladhī","yanhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,1980],[3,1980,2915]]}},{"name":"96:10","price":"9-10. (நபியே!) ஓர் அடியார் தொழுதால், அதைத் தடை செய்கின்றவனை நீர் (கவனித்துப்) பார்த்தீரா?","arabic":"عَبۡدًا إِذَا صَلَّىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6116,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿabdan idhā ṣallā ","translations":["A slave","when","he prays","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿabdan","idhā","ṣallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1500],[3,1500,2545]]}},{"name":"96:11","price":"11-12. அவர் நேரான பாதையில் இருந்துகொண்டு, இறையச்சத்தை ஏவிக்கொண்டிருந்தும் (அவரை அவன் தடை செய்வதை) நீர் (கவனித்துப்) பார்த்தீரா?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ إِن كَانَ عَلَى ٱلۡهُدَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6117,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ara-ayta in kāna ʿalā al-hudā ","translations":["Have you seen","if","he is","upon","[the] guidance","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["ara-ayta","in","kāna","ʿalā","al-hudā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,990],[2,990,2050],[3,2050,2720],[4,2720,3040],[5,3040,4055]]}},{"name":"96:12","price":"11-12. அவர் நேரான பாதையில் இருந்துகொண்டு, இறையச்சத்தை ஏவிக்கொண்டிருந்தும் (அவரை அவன் தடை செய்வதை) நீர் (கவனித்துப்) பார்த்தீரா?","arabic":"أَوۡ أَمَرَ بِٱلتَّقۡوَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6118,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"aw amara bil-taqwā ","translations":["Or","he enjoins","[of the] righteousness","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["aw","amara","bil-taqwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,440],[2,440,1100],[3,1100,2475]]}},{"name":"96:13","price":"13. (அவன், அவரைப்) பொய்யாக்கிப் புறக்கணிப்பதையும் நீர் கவனித்தீரா?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ إِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6119,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ara-ayta in kadhaba watawallā ","translations":["Have you seen","if","he denies","and turns away","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["ara-ayta","in","kadhaba","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,2090],[3,2090,2930],[4,2930,4195]]}},{"name":"96:14","price":"14. (அவன் செய்யும் இந்த துஷ்ட காரியங்களை) நிச்சயமாக அல்லாஹ் பார்க்கிறான் என்பதை அவன் அறிந்து கொள்ளவில்லையா?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ يَعۡلَم بِأَنَّ ٱللَّهَ يَرَىٰ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6120,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alam yaʿlam bi-anna al-laha yarā ","translations":["Does not","he know","that","Allah","sees","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","yaʿlam","bi-anna","al-laha","yarā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,2160],[3,2160,3620],[4,3620,4440],[5,4440,5545]]}},{"name":"96:15","price":"15, 16. (இவ்வாறு அவன் செய்வது) தகாது; (இந்த துஷ்ட செயலிலிருந்து) அவன் விலகிக் கொள்ளாவிடில், குற்றம் செய்யும் அப்பொய்யனின் முன் குடுமியைப் பிடித்து நாம் இழுப்போம்.","arabic":"كَلَّا لَئِن لَّمۡ يَنتَهِ لَنَسۡفَعَۢا بِٱلنَّاصِيَةِ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6121,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā la-in lam yantahi lanasfaʿan bil-nāṣiyati ","translations"